[Civ. No. 6994. Second Appellate District, Division One. October 17, 1929.] FRANK GUBIN et al., Petitioners, v. SUPERIOR COURT OF LOS ANGELES COUNTY, Respondent.

Paul Schenck for Petitioners.

No appearance for Respondent.

THE COURT.

The petition for writ of prohibition is denied. (Williams v. Chadbourne, 6 Cal. 559; Crocker v. Conrey, 140 Cal. 213 [73 Pac. 1006]; Bar Association v. Superior Court, 64 Cal. App. 590 [222 Pac. 185].)
